cast.overview: The extraordinary tale of Harriet Tubman's escape from slavery and transformation into one of America's greatest heroes. Her courage, ingenuity and tenacity freed hundreds of slaves and changed the course of history.
cast.title: Harriet

details.biography: Joseph Lee Anderson is an American actor, writer, and director. He's known for his roles as Benji in Tyler Perry's Divorce in the Black, Rocky Johnson on NBC's Young Rock, Davids in The 24th, Robert Ross in Harriet, and Oak in The Ballad of Lefty Brown.
details.name: Joseph Lee Anderson
